Source: minibook-dual-accelerometer
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Petrus Claviger <noreply@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-dkms

Package: minibook-dual-accelerometer
Architecture: all
Depends: dkms, linux-headers-amd64, python3, python3-numpy, python3-pyudev
Description: Dual accelerometer support for Chuwi MiniBook N150
 Provides a DKMS kernel module (chuwi-ltsm-hack) that exposes both
 accelerometers on the Chuwi MiniBook, plus a userspace daemon that
 computes the hinge angle and toggles tablet mode accordingly.
